{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to a world consumed by darkness. Take charge of the fight against the Lord of Darkness, whose army of skeletons spreads chaos and destruction. This is a turn-based strategy game with a deep storyline, where every decision you make impacts not only the outcome of battles but the fate of the entire world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to challenge the darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/\u041e\u043f\u0438\u0441\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435.png?t=1736520831\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cinematic storytelling:</strong> The story comes to life through stunning cutscenes that highlight key moments in the narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/gif1.gif?t=1736520831\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>An epic tale of light versus darkness:</strong> Free the lands from terrifying skeleton hordes and restore hope to a world ravaged by war and magic.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic and tactical battles:</strong> Analyze the battlefield, devise your strategy, and use your heroes\u2019 abilities to find your enemies\u2019 weaknesses and achieve victory, even in the toughest fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/gif2.gif?t=1736520831\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The fight against the dark army:</strong> Face endless waves of undead skeletons\u2014from simple soldiers to powerful bosses. Each enemy presents unique challenges, making every battle feel distinct.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Atmospheric locations:</strong> Explore the ruins of ancient temples, shadowy forests, dungeons, and lands scorched by darkness.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The End of Darkness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/58fc147d71d6e85fa483224c5c178ca5e41a1f4f.jpg"},{"name":"The Dark Priestess Falls","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/cc6cd8ba70853a25de87da52c915b8e7c50c5c6f.jpg"},{"name":"The Fall of Xaphan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/8095dcdc32dc68859600d096b596da583fc62802.jpg"},{"name":"Stone Shatterer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/a6157ce52884f223f5ff63518d15e2632e1a827d.jpg"},{"name":"Demon Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/1a280ba64e782eaeee56d7e71023fd441d68fc7a.jpg"},{"name":"Elara became strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/55ac76239adcdce726b9067fbe85b55cff03fa2b.jpg"},{"name":"Liam became strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/4c7ef92d6497e0f2a6076aa2a81208a18fef73f5.jpg"},{"name":"Seraphima became strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/61bde4bb6dbcda8cc05acfc9001197b007f085c7.jpg"},{"name":"Alister became strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/3146f150d900d5542deb169df0c03c3d4a994d2d.jpg"},{"name":"Keil became strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3302960/286554cbd0e318365f721b68d8ca785892751522.jpg"}],"total":25},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736520831","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat